{"tid":1747914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我想恭喜定葵芳選區建制派先","createTime":"2019-11-23T12:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T14:03:01.000Z","uid":280724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a561cbd49d6411cbc3d5e01c360d79cba8fec88c","tid":1747914,"uid":280724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:11:02.000Z","msg":"因為啲人話：<br />\n死都唔投白頭佬（白頭佬從來錯不在區議會議席）<br />\n投倒區選對運動無幫助（要唔諗野就自然諗唔倒有乜幫助）<br />\n<br />\n多謝你地射落海，預祝建制派先取一席<br />\n<br />\n最後，真心話，希望我係燒山"},{"pid":"02f84866865244e90c815e7db79ec64bf3a99981","tid":1747914,"uid":183520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"如果我係葵芳人都一定會投佢<br />\n但港共壯大任意妄為真係由佢唔肯做主席開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69295f0f4482cb14af9fdf715c40c6c1fe921255","tid":1747914,"uid":282836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"【11-24 告急】 投本土泛民，不投建制，連登每小時245留言討論投對家，有圖<br />\n<br />\n11月23日 9am<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0W3121w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0W3121w.png&h=8e86a76e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n11月23日 6pm後 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3kjHNsX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3kjHNsX.png&h=77dee4e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n詳情幫推這個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezKeyS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezKeyS</a>"},{"pid":"64e2d7ba565ced731f1eea3e314718708c6fd443","tid":1747914,"uid":280724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f84866865244e90c815e7db79ec64bf3a99981","tid":1747914,"uid":183520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"如果我係葵芳人都一定會投佢<br />\n但港共壯大任意妄為真係由佢唔肯做主席開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:01:55.000Z","msg":"之前連登去扮藍叫藍絲唔好投票從來無有人信過<br />\n只有黃呢邊啲人會自己信左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係果句，佢鳩係鳩在唔係做大事搞政治做立法會議員嘅材料，但區議會唔洗理咁多，而街工地區以往都有口碑<br />\n<br />\n屌死建制派之前，乜鳩我都唔理，非建制乜鳩都投，非建制坐得大將來先有機會揀心水人選"},{"pid":"a3afb4e8dd21136dcd8d653323be7469e141a14e","tid":1747914,"uid":280724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T14:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/65nNZoX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F65nNZoX.jpg&h=f28ed89e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}